Nathan King (born 29 August 1970) is an English musician. Currently a member of Level 42, King has performed with Frost*, It Bites, and The Blockheads. He is the younger brother of Level 42's Mark King.
King is also a contributor to the "All About the Bass" series on the Andertons TV YouTube channel.
